{"body": ":+1: This restricts the appending of `[]` to the name *only* if the name option was not specified. \r\n\r\nThe bug is the line `options[\"name\"] += \"[]\" if options[\"multiple\"] && !options[\"name\"].ends_with?(\"[]\")` -- which appends the `[]` suffix even if a name was explicitly specified. That was a bad thing.\r\n\r\nAgree that this is the correct solution to #9830. Looks good.", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/15974476", "created_at": "2013-04-05T19:04:30Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/10105#issuecomment-15974476", "updated_at": "2013-04-05T19:04:47Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 10105, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/trisweb/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/trisweb/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/trisweb/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/trisweb", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/trisweb/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/trisweb", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/trisweb/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://2.gravatar.com/avatar/eb97c4cc97698ed0b22918225d178761?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F9ce08f4789d775aaeeac87805dd89284.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/trisweb/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/trisweb/received_events", "gravatar_id": "eb97c4cc97698ed0b22918225d178761", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/trisweb/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "trisweb", "type": "User", "id": 89588, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/trisweb/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "5237e317bd3543c1510090af"}, "id": 15974476, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/10105"}
